# The list of vouched (or actively denounced) users for this repository.
#
# Maintainers can vouch for new contributors by commenting "!vouch @user"
# on an issue or PR. Denounce with "!denounce @user reason" and remove
# with "!unvouch @user".
#
# Syntax:
#  - One handle per line (without @), sorted alphabetically.
#  - Prefix with minus to denounce: -username [optional reason]
#  - Comments start with #.
dogancanbakir
